      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know you aren't a doc but it feels so much like my usual migraines just way more intense. the face thing is weird but maybe it's just like aura or something? i really don't want to sit in an ER for 8 hours if i can just help it myself. do you think if i take the triptan and maybe some ibuprofen it'll kick in fast enough to make this go away?",
